full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/2/2023 -2- look after their landed property during whole of the Second World war. After the war ended it became known that he was missing after the reoccupation of Rangoon by the British. I have been informed that there was no witness or report available from the British administrative Authorities. Whatever I have stated above is true. Navsari.
